metadata.name: Sunset - Artist/Collabs
metadata.description:
Holders of "Sunset" will always get one free claim (1 Token/art) if available, early access to mint, allow list/whitelist if available for any collabs Digivatar is doing with other artists. 

A snapshot of current (Sunset) holders will always be made before these collaborative projects drop/mint so holders can be added to such lists.
